      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "EDGE OF FAITH (1) produced a moderate effort last time when sixth at this track over 330m behind Fenella (19.41) in a Grade 5. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings four times from five attempts. Can discover winning form. CAWBOURNE GIGI (3) was sent out at big odds from this same box last time but ran above herself when a 2.75 lengths second (18.63) at Wagga in Grade 5. With a good start should be able to take advantage of the low draw. Worth another try. LITTLE KING (4) missed the frame and was safely held latest finishing 7th at this track following on from a third place finish (19.27) there the start prior. The form from his last run stacks up well. Expected to run well. INDECISION (2) is in the mix despite finishing out of the placings here last start.",
